es cleanses and correlates large amounts of customer data from various sources and standard it operating model and taxonomy that provides a standard model for how it costs are captured categorized and allocated to it services and business services its solution also comprises visual modeling which allows users to build a apptio inc provides cloudbased technology business management tbm solutions to enterprises its cloudbased platform and saas applications enable it leaders to analyze optimize and plan technology investments and to benchmark their financial and operational performance against peers the company’s tbm solutions consist of adaptive data management which aggregates cleanses and correlates large amounts of customer data from various sources and standard it operating model and taxonomy that provides a standard model for how it costs are captured categorized and allocated to it services and business services its solution also comprises visual modeling which allows users to build and manage the financial and operational model of their it organization powerful calculation engine that allows the models to be applied across very large data sets accessible to users through the analytics capabilities included in its applications intuitive selfservice analytics for it and business users and modular applications comprising cost transparency it benchmarking business insights bill of it and it planning applications the company operates in the united states the united kingdom germany denmark the netherlands canada australia france and singapore apptio inc was founded in  and is headquartered in bellevue washington detailed description  ne th streetsuite bellevue wa united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwapptiocom key executives for apptio inc mr sachin gupta cofounder ceo president  director age  total annual compensation k mr kurt shintaffer cofounder  cfo age  total annual compensation k mr john morrow executive vp of corporate development general counsel  secretary age  total annual compensation k mr christopher pick chief marketing officer age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  apptio inc key developments apptio inc appoints kathleen philips as director jun   on may   the board of directors of apptio inc increased the size of the board to eight directors and appointed kathleen philips to serve as a director of the company with the appointment effective immediately ms philips has been with zillow group inc since  and has served as zillow groups chief financial officer and treasurer since august  chief legal officer since september  and secretary since july  ms philips has also been appointed to serve on the audit committee and compensation committee of the company apptio inc selected as one of seven cloud service providers for fedramp connect program may   apptio inc announced that one of seven cloud service providers selected for the fedramp connect program through participation in this program apptio will be prioritized for fedramp certification based on demand from cios across the federal government fedramp connect is a new initiative developed by fedramp working closely with the federal cio council and omb of the  vendors that applied for fedramp connect only seven were selected based on their governmentwide demand applicability for crossagency use and the security of their system the federal risk and authorization management program fedramp is a governmentwide program that provides a standardized approach to security assessment authorization and continuous monitoring for cloud products and services apptio inc presents at th annual jp morgan global technology media and telecom conference may  am may   apptio inc presents at th annual jp morgan global technology media and telecom conference may  am venue westin copley place  huntington ave boston massachusetts united states speakers sachin gupta cofounder chief executive officer president and director similar private companies by industry com